  "body": "### Description\nPicoCLI supports adding section headings to the help text output: https://picocli.info/quick-guide.html#_section_headings\n\nWe should investigate what is actually required to do this and utilise it in teku's help text since we now have a lot of options which can be overwhelming as a single big list.\n\nBesu has been doing this recently so it may be worth leaning from the PRs linked to issue https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/issues/2757",
